Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Wow! This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:11.15,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Look at all the yachts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:13.78,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far we could go on that one of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet we could even go to another country!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because this place opens out into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wanna ride on one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:24.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gettin' kinda hungry, so let's hurry back and grab some lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should've known Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} only cared about his stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that looks {\i1}so{\i0} good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you taking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm from the Shirakabe Hotel.\NI brought the food you ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:00:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he's from a hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So of course it would look delicious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm not going to give you some just for looking. Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't say something so unkind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.63,0:01:16.05,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nao Takiguchi (34)\NWife of the Company President
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:15.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all your effort. That was quite fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a cute doggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Coro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's a really pretty necklace, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this is just a cheap thing, made of acrylic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, ma'am, but where should I put your food?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. Could I have you carry it on to the ship for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you guys are also welcome to come aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't go with a stranger...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The food from this hotel is very delicious. Don't you want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if we eat some, you won't have enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You children don't need to be so hesitant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:55.30,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kōtarō Takiguchi (55)\NCompany President
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:55.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You could probably even have dinner too with all the food we ordered!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we can really eat with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. We were thinking it would be lonely with just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's our pleasure to invite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, we'll gladly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Accept your treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:15.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We won't give in to the hot blazing sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A gallant and dashing deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.45,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All of us become eyewitnesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...to the rich man who dove straight into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:22.62,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.24,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid, but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:27.33,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez. Where did those guys run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your fault for sleeping ever since we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we still can't find them after looking a little longer, I'm eating their lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be sorry if you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grudges over food can be pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too bad Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} can't eat any of this delicious food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's their fault for coming out to the beach and just sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have other friends here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're very close, but Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said she didn't want to get sunburnt today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:05:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she worries about her skin that much as a primary schooler...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to seeing what a beauty she'll become in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even though Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s in primary school,\Nhe stays up all night reading mystery novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a kid, but he really doesn't act like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{He \i1so \i0doesn't act cute.}It's really annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Well, sorry for not acting cute.}Well, sorry for being annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that cute girl down there is Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:23.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Though I apologise for not being a "beauty" yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're very beautiful, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For a primary school student, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I should be asking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came looking for you because we thought we should eat our lunches soon, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologise to your mothers who took the time to make them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's fine as long as you can eat them before going home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two, come on up and eat with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, come on! This roast beef's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this spiny lobster's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko, you're eating too much lobster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you this is {\i1}spiny {\i0}lobster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The children will laugh at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're almost like newlyweds!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We only got married six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I say that, but this is also my first marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so busy expanding my company...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot about getting married until I was this old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be so wonderful if we could take this ship out,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and swim around in the pretty ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't swim very well on your own yet, can you, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had a boat like this at home, I'd learn to swim super fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let it get you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't swim either, until I was this age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after some practice, I finally learnt how.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a person puts their mind to it,\Nthey can accomplish anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you went to a sports club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Our house was just built, so I seized the opportunity and had a pool built.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll show you something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were recording me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop. It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in the end... See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really did learn how to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's race and see who gets to that bank first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can use a swim ring, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just had wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if you hadn't, your blood pressure's high.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should have a rest before swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aww, and I was sure I'd win, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How old is Coro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just turned one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The buckle on his collar is rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. Maybe that's because we take him on walks, even on rainy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, we should head back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Going off and having a feast all by themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's what they were doing, why didn't someone come let me know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was really worried, and was thinking of calling the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eating while angry is bad for your digestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heads up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Nao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and her husband's ship heading out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep! Nao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are they planning on swimming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister! Thanks for the food earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go swimming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go get a swim ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?! This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone... Anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! He's drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{This is very worrying, isn't it?}I'm worried now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kinda don't feel like playing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The day's still young, but let's head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fire station will want to question us about Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} by phone later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You five. Aren't you the kids who were with Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to pick up the dishes, but it didn't look like there was anyone on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, then we'll go get the dishes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So you couldn't ride in the ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we bring Nao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and her husband their clothes and things?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.65,Signs,,0,0,0,,Emergency Medical Centre
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're sure this was an accident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There hasn't been a thorough investigation yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:48.62,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ryōichi Katagiri (48)\NTakaguchi's Secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But according to the witnesses' statements, there appears to be no doubt that he dove into the water on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.62,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:54.54,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Detective Nagai (38)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:48.62,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Couldn't someone have pushed him off or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:52.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He and his wife were the only ones on board the ship at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:55.13,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Are you saying his wife pushed him overboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the president told me this himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he was a child, he almost drowned in a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been afraid of water ever since, and couldn't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He recently practised and learnt how to swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're kids who met the Takiguchis at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came because they say they're very grateful to those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We brought their clothes, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Coro had been left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} doing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a hard thing to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but his death was confirmed just a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! To think that such a good man could die...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please look into it and find out whether or not this was really an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Even before we got married, I'm certain people were after our fortune."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president told me that more times than I can count!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, the president was completely deceived by that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to think that it would end like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying that Nao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s a bad person?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way someone so nice would ever do something bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please excuse them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you from Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s company?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm Katagiri, the head secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all witnessed the accident, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} drown right before our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} waved at us, and then dove into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, while it may be difficult on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,can I have you come to the police station and give us the details of what happened then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, when Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} dove in,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,do you know where his wife was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was standing not too far from him, doing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was probably cleaning up the dishes from lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that would explain why she took a while to notice he was drowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for bringing me my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, your necklace...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I bet that when I rescued him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the chain snapped, and it sunk into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard the story from these kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's apparent that your husband dove into the sea by his own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems we weren't mistaken in thinking that this was an unfortunate accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my own fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how well he said he'd learnt to swim...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had only warned him a little harder...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:14:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you just one more thing about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told people at his company that he couldn't swim...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So did he really learn how to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why not show him that practice video?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I recorded this when he first started practising in the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.50,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.63,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Keep moving towards me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:25.09,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The parts where I'm in the video were filmed by our maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then this was recorded last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.81,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.98,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't stop, try a flip turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really was learning to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come with me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I see your video camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something important in that video?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.59,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:11.30,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yep! Nao{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10} came out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good. It picked up the audio, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is what happens next...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:20.60,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's go swimming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:21.56,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.19,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then I'll go get a swim ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:26.02,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is this?! This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:28.94,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Someone... Anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can this zoom in more?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, though the picture gets blurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:41.92,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Someone... Anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.30,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:58.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's a brief period between when Nao{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} realised Kōtarō{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} was drowning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:01.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and when she jumped in to rescue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:06.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Besides, that cruiser had a life preserver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So why didn't she use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:15.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What was that thing I saw in the background of his swimming practice video?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was Kōtarō{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} actually...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you two whispering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.50,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The buckle on his collar is rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:33.49,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh. Maybe that's because we take him on walks, even on rainy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for having inconvenienced you,\Nbut you're all free to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to the hospital, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I have you wait on that a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have something you wish to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:58.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is no mere accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is a meticulously planned murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} dove into the sea on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed. However, if he knew that he couldn't swim,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} probably wouldn't have dove in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} couldn't swim, he had been put under the impression that he could,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and suddenly led out into the open sea in his cruiser, where his feet couldn't touch the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a perfect murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so, Nao Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband really could swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:40.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw that too, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So are you saying that that video was manipulated somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that video is perfectly genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} {\i1}could{\i0} swim...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...but only in his own pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lemme borrow this a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at Nao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s necklace here, when her husband was practising his flutter kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There. You see how it's submerged in the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But on the last day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? It floats on the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! L-Let me see that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're right. The necklace wasn't floating, but now it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I have you explain, in simpler terms, what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did the necklace float?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I learnt that from Coro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though Coro only just turned one year old,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for some reason, the buckle on his collar is rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because the victim's wife put a large quantity of bath salts into the pool water,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in order to make his body float more easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The necklace in the video is made of acrylic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The specific gravity of acrylic is about 1.17 to 1.2.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meaning the water in the pool last week had a higher specific gravity than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong. If I'd put that much bath salts in the water,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,even my thickheaded husband would have realised it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what {\i1}did{\i0} you put in the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The necklace that was submerged in the sea was floating in the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, your own video proves that the specific gravity of the pool water was higher than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we go to your home and check?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you did go, there's no water in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we already drained the pool water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mustn't underestimate the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as there's the slightest bit of residue in the pool,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they'll find out right away what was dissolved in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, is what this man is saying true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! It's not true, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's... true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I put bath salts in the water at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I started adding more, he figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, I switched to a water-soluble polymer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A non-toxic one, used in medicines and foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The specific gravity of the pool water last week was probably over 1.3.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For reference, 1.3 is about the same as the Dead Sea, where it's said that you can float on the surface and read a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it wouldn't be unreasonable for Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to believe he could swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably recorded that video,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,thinking you could use it when the police questioned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But on the contrary, that video became your undoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Up until now, that man's head had been filled with nothing but thoughts of expanding his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:21:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was fine with using any dirty means necessary to do so,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and didn't care how many people he made unhappy as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why this time, I wanted to teach him how it felt to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the agony of living with that unrefined man who lacked any common decency
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was just too much to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at the limits of what I could handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While it may be true that Takiguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was obsessed with earning money,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and lacked common decency and refinement,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,don't you think he's still a much better person than you, who killed someone out of revenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believed that she was a kind person, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know. I thought she was a good person when she treated us to lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm never trusting a grown-up ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are all kinds of adults. All kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Even now, I still have a pure, untainted heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Did you just laugh because I said it's pure?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Didn't we still have the lunches we brought?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! Thanks to us being treated this afternoon, we still have our lunches!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:33.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up and eat 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I'm pretty hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what the side dish is today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eel, eel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:41.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you guys {\i1}just{\i0} feeling down in the dumps?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right! She's even holding Tai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This cat is my granddaughter's cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.15,0:23:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These two men turned up claiming to be his owners too...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm his real owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! I'm telling you, he's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not that ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...with a mystery solving specialist at my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.80,0:24:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: The Case of the Beckoning Calico Cat (Part I)!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Taii!
